nodes.text: Ascendant of Mau was a title held by Nartun Trecim according to Collected Poems, Prayers, and Meditations on the Force, a compilation of writings on the Force edited by the Disciple of the Whills Kozem Pel.
The title Ascendant of Mau was first used in the novel Guardians of the Whills, which was written by Greg Rucka and released on May 2, 2017.
